* DAYTIM. - GIVE DATE AND TIME MMDDYY HHMM.M
       PCC     ON 
       NOLNK
       ENTRY   DAYTIM   
       LBL     TIME     
       PCC     OFF
*     
*  CALLING SEQUENCE IS  
*      TSX     DAYTIM,4 
*      TXH     DATE     
*      TXH     TIME     
*     
DAYTIM SCA     TX4,4         SAVE XR4.    
       TSX     GETIME,4      GET DATE AND TIME. 
       SLW     TIME          ..     
       LAC     TX4,4         RESTORE XR4. 
       STQ*    1,4           RETURN DATE. 
       LDQ     TIME          CONVERT TIME.
       ZAC                   ..     
       DVP     =360          GET RID OF SMALL FRACTIONS.    
       ZAC                   ..     
       DVP     =10           GET 1/10 MIN.
       ORA     =O3300        ..     
       SLW     HHMM.M        ..     
       ZAC                   ..     
       DVP     =10           GET SINGLE MIN.    
       ALS     12            SHIFT TO POSITION. 
       ORS     HHMM.M        ..     
       ZAC                   ..     
       DVP     =6            GET 10'S MIN.
       ALS     18            SHIFT. 
       ORS     HHMM.M        ..     
       ZAC                   ..     
       DVP     =24           ONLY 24 HRS. 
       XCA                   ..     
       ZAC                   ..     
       DVP     =10           GET SINGLE HRS.    
       ALS     24            SHIFT. 
       ORS     HHMM.M        ..     
       XCA                   10'S OF HRS ARE LEFT.    
       ALS     30            SHIFT. 
       ORA     HHMM.M        OR IN REST OF TIME.
TX4    AXC     -,4           ..     
       SLW*    2,4           ..     
       TRA     3,4           RETURN.
       REM
       REM
HHMM.M PZE  
TIME   PZE  
       REM
GETIME TIA     =HGETIME 
       REM
       END  
